---
title: Grilled Meatloaf Burgers with Foil Pouch Potatoes and Green Onion Mayo
description: The best of mom's meatloaf and a classic beef burger combine between toasted brioche buns! Zesty green onion mayo is a great dipper for BBQ foil pouch potatoes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-grilles-au-pain-de-viande-de3cfca4.jpg
